WEBVTT

1
00:00:10.038 --> 00:00:11.164
THIS SERIES IS FICTITIOUS

2
00:00:11.247 --> 00:00:13.875
CHILDREN WERE FILMED SAFELY
GEN AI WAS USED IN SELECT SCENES

3
00:00:50.245 --> 00:00:52.205
{\an8}EPISODE 3

4
00:02:03.610 --> 00:02:05.153
This way! Move!

5
00:02:06.696 --> 00:02:07.822
Hayun.

6
00:02:07.906 --> 00:02:09.574
Oh. my God. Hayun.

7
00:02:12.577 --> 00:02:13.912
Wait. Doctor.

8
00:02:13.995 --> 00:02:16.080
Can you wait until Dr. Kang gets here?

9
00:02:16.831 --> 00:02:18.333
We don't have time.

10
00:02:18.416 --> 00:02:20.627
Bone fragments
from her broken cervical vertebrae

11
00:02:20.710 --> 00:02:22.462
are compressing her respiratory center.

12
00:02:22.545 --> 00:02:25.507
If we don't operate right now.
she's going into respiratory arrest.

13
00:02:26.090 --> 00:02:27.425
We'll try our best.

14
00:02:27.509 --> 00:02:29.552
Ms. Ko. I have to ask you
to wait out here.

15
00:02:36.184 --> 00:02:40.313
WOORI TOGETHER MEDICAL CENTER

16
00:02:40.396 --> 00:02:42.148
CALLING
HUSBAND

17
00:02:43.775 --> 00:02:46.569
Come on. honey. pick up.

18
00:02:46.653 --> 00:02:48.196
Please. Hayun is…

19
00:02:51.199 --> 00:02:53.201
Why won't he pick up?

20
00:02:54.994 --> 00:02:56.663
Where on earth is he?

21
00:02:59.374 --> 00:03:00.375
Blade.

22
00:03:05.463 --> 00:03:06.589
Bovie. please.

23
00:03:39.580 --> 00:03:40.581
Vitals are dropping.

24
00:03:41.499 --> 00:03:42.667
Give me an amp of epi.

25
00:03:54.679 --> 00:03:56.681
Oh. please…

26
00:04:01.311 --> 00:04:02.395
She's flatlining!

27
00:04:11.195 --> 00:04:13.448
The patient is flatlining.
Keep compressions going.

28
00:04:14.324 --> 00:04:15.533
Get the crash cart in here!

29
00:04:48.483 --> 00:04:51.027
Ms. Ko. we're sorry.

30
00:04:51.986 --> 00:04:53.613
We did our best. but…

31
00:05:30.650 --> 00:05:31.859
Dr. Kang.

32
00:05:31.943 --> 00:05:33.736
RESTRICTED AREA
AUTHORIZED PERSONNEL ONLY

33
00:05:50.795 --> 00:05:52.296
Where have you been?

34
00:06:08.354 --> 00:06:11.691
I said. where have you been?

35
00:06:19.574 --> 00:06:21.659
Where have you been?

36
00:06:26.622 --> 00:06:28.374
Answer me!

37
00:06:29.876 --> 00:06:32.503
Where the hell have you been?

38
00:06:34.297 --> 00:06:35.298
While…

39
00:06:38.759 --> 00:06:42.847
Where were you while our Hayun was dying?

40
00:06:51.981 --> 00:06:53.441
This is all your fault.

41
00:06:56.402 --> 00:06:58.112
It's all your fault.

42
00:07:04.160 --> 00:07:05.953
This whole thing is your fault.

43
00:07:10.249 --> 00:07:12.919
This is all your fault!

44
00:07:17.632 --> 00:07:22.553
THE HUSBAND

45
00:07:24.639 --> 00:07:27.016
SEONGJIN POLICE STATION

46
00:07:27.099 --> 00:07:29.101
<i>How do you know the kidnapper?</i>

47
00:07:30.520 --> 00:07:31.979
I don't know him.

48
00:07:32.939 --> 00:07:35.399
He showed up when I called for a driver.

49
00:07:35.483 --> 00:07:37.527
So you solicited

50
00:07:38.402 --> 00:07:40.238
a complete stranger to murder your wife?

51
00:07:40.905 --> 00:07:42.573
I never solicited anything.

52
00:07:42.657 --> 00:07:45.952
Mr. Kang. where's your accomplice?

53
00:07:48.538 --> 00:07:50.665
I really don't know.
I didn't put him up to it.

54
00:07:50.748 --> 00:07:52.416
Tell us. You know where she is!

55
00:07:52.500 --> 00:07:55.503
I said I don't know!

56
00:07:55.586 --> 00:07:57.171
Your accomplice…

57
00:07:57.255 --> 00:08:00.424
He's way more dangerous than you think.

58
00:08:00.508 --> 00:08:02.635
You're going to end up
taking the fall alone.

59
00:08:03.261 --> 00:08:07.765
Just how many times do I have to tell you?

60
00:08:08.516 --> 00:08:10.560
You're losing time here!

61
00:08:11.435 --> 00:08:15.314
Do you have any idea
what a waste of time this is?

62
00:08:15.815 --> 00:08:19.026
This guy is a psycho!
My wife is in danger!

63
00:08:19.110 --> 00:08:20.111
Calm down. Mr. Kang.

64
00:08:20.194 --> 00:08:21.320
I'm serious!

65
00:08:21.863 --> 00:08:24.365
There's no time to be screwing around!

66
00:08:24.448 --> 00:08:25.449
Mr. Kang!

67
00:08:32.373 --> 00:08:33.749
Calm now?

68
00:08:36.043 --> 00:08:38.796
Wash your face off.
And freshen up a little.

69
00:08:38.880 --> 00:08:40.339
That one doesn't work.

70
00:08:40.423 --> 00:08:41.591
Use the next one.

71
00:08:43.801 --> 00:08:45.219
What the hell?

72
00:08:45.303 --> 00:08:49.640
Man. it's about time
they fix this place up.

73
00:08:49.724 --> 00:08:51.225
Nothing works in here.

74
00:08:55.354 --> 00:08:56.981
Hey. Captain Kim.

75
00:08:57.064 --> 00:08:59.692
Yeah. It's been too long.

76
00:09:00.192 --> 00:09:02.069
Oh. that? Yeah. it was really helpful.

77
00:09:02.153 --> 00:09:03.279
Take your time. okay?

78
00:09:03.821 --> 00:09:07.241
Right. I was going to come and see you.

79
00:09:09.327 --> 00:09:11.662
Come on. not this again.

80
00:09:13.122 --> 00:09:15.041
What the hell. man?

81
00:09:15.124 --> 00:09:17.001
SEONGJIN POLICE STATION

82
00:09:17.084 --> 00:09:19.420
SAFE SEONGJIN. TRUSTED POLICE

83
00:09:20.546 --> 00:09:23.466
I didn't do it.
but everyone thinks I did.

84
00:09:25.051 --> 00:09:27.053
No one believes me.

85
00:09:28.137 --> 00:09:29.430
Who would?

86
00:09:33.684 --> 00:09:34.977
No one believes you.

87
00:09:36.604 --> 00:09:38.856
Why would anyone believe you. Mr. Kang?

88
00:09:43.486 --> 00:09:44.904
Who are you?

89
00:09:49.700 --> 00:09:51.035
I said. who are you?

90
00:09:52.244 --> 00:09:57.375
I'm the only one who knows
you didn't plot your wife's death.

91
00:10:00.336 --> 00:10:01.337
What?

92
00:10:09.011 --> 00:10:10.096
Mr. Kang.

93
00:10:14.475 --> 00:10:15.476
Mr. Kang.

94
00:10:16.268 --> 00:10:17.520
Mr. Kang!

95
00:10:20.064 --> 00:10:22.900
-Mr. Kang!
-Oh. yes. I'm right here.

96
00:10:22.984 --> 00:10:24.527
Why didn't you answer any…

97
00:10:25.236 --> 00:10:26.404
You going to be a while?

98
00:10:26.904 --> 00:10:28.030
Little bit. yeah.

99
00:10:28.864 --> 00:10:31.283
Power's out. but don't panic.

100
00:10:31.367 --> 00:10:32.868
And make it quick.

101
00:10:32.952 --> 00:10:34.829
Okay. I got it. Sorry.

102
00:10:57.685 --> 00:10:58.686
So who are you?

103
00:11:02.648 --> 00:11:05.151
How do you know
I didn't have my wife kidnapped?

104
00:11:06.694 --> 00:11:09.989
What's important isn't how I know.

105
00:11:10.781 --> 00:11:12.908
but whether your wife is alive
or not right now.

106
00:11:14.827 --> 00:11:16.245
What?

107
00:11:16.328 --> 00:11:19.373
I doubt there's anyone you can trust
besides me right now.

108
00:11:21.584 --> 00:11:23.127
Who the hell are you?

109
00:11:24.545 --> 00:11:25.629
I told you.

110
00:11:26.338 --> 00:11:30.801
I'm the only one who knows
you didn't have your wife kidnapped.

111
00:11:32.344 --> 00:11:35.139
Or rather. I'm the only one
who can help you.

112
00:11:39.351 --> 00:11:40.352
So…

113
00:11:41.395 --> 00:11:44.231
Seyun is alive. right?

114
00:11:45.441 --> 00:11:46.859
Where is she right now?

115
00:11:47.735 --> 00:11:52.698
If you want to find your wife.
come to 543-7. Shinyu-dong by 11 p.m.

116
00:11:54.241 --> 00:11:55.534
What was that?

117
00:11:55.618 --> 00:11:56.619
If you don't.

118
00:11:57.536 --> 00:11:59.455
you may never get to see her again.

119
00:11:59.538 --> 00:12:03.959
Look. man.
I'm being held here as a suspect.

120
00:12:04.043 --> 00:12:06.087
How am I supposed to get there by 11 p.m.?

121
00:12:07.046 --> 00:12:08.422
Remember.

122
00:12:09.423 --> 00:12:12.593
It's 543-7. Shinyu-dong.
Get there by 11 p.m.

123
00:12:20.810 --> 00:12:22.186
For God's sake.

124
00:12:43.249 --> 00:12:45.376
Hayun. Mommy's right here.

125
00:12:50.214 --> 00:12:52.174
Yeah. Hayun. Mommy's right…

126
00:13:24.790 --> 00:13:26.250
<i>There's no time.</i>

127
00:13:26.333 --> 00:13:28.127
<i>I'm running out of time.</i>

128
00:13:29.128 --> 00:13:33.507
<i>When the girl in the red hood
gets swallowed by the snow…</i>

129
00:13:34.383 --> 00:13:35.759
<i>It's over.</i>

130
00:13:41.640 --> 00:13:44.685
-Come on. Mom. Hurry!
-Oh. geez.

131
00:13:46.896 --> 00:13:49.899
This way. Over there.
He's on the second floor. Come on.

132
00:13:49.982 --> 00:13:52.318
ALWAYS WITH THE PEOPLE
SEONGJIN POLICE STATION

133
00:13:53.903 --> 00:13:54.904
Mom.

134
00:13:56.113 --> 00:14:01.827
Excuse me. we got a call
saying my son was being held here.

135
00:14:01.911 --> 00:14:04.496
-What's your son's name?
-Taeju. Kang Taeju.

136
00:14:04.580 --> 00:14:06.832
Mr. Kang is in interrogation
at the moment.

137
00:14:06.916 --> 00:14:08.208
-What?
-What?

138
00:14:08.292 --> 00:14:10.544
But my brother didn't do anything wrong.

139
00:14:10.628 --> 00:14:14.089
How's my brother the suspect
when his wife's been kidnapped?

140
00:14:14.173 --> 00:14:18.010
Look. sir.
My son would never commit a crime.

141
00:14:18.093 --> 00:14:20.220
This has to be a mistake.

142
00:14:20.304 --> 00:14:22.097
It's not a mistake.

143
00:14:28.604 --> 00:14:30.189
Mr. Ko.

144
00:14:31.190 --> 00:14:32.858
I said. it's not a mistake.

145
00:14:39.949 --> 00:14:41.533
I'm a parent too.

146
00:14:43.285 --> 00:14:46.121
I know you must be heartbroken.

147
00:14:47.206 --> 00:14:49.375
But you know what my Taeju is like

148
00:14:49.917 --> 00:14:51.961
just as well as I do.

149
00:14:52.503 --> 00:14:56.215
Yeah. absolutely.
I know what kind of scum he is.

150
00:14:56.298 --> 00:15:01.220
The despicable kind that plotted
to have my daughter killed.

151
00:15:01.303 --> 00:15:02.346
Excuse me?

152
00:15:05.891 --> 00:15:08.644
I know this is hard. but that's just…

153
00:15:10.688 --> 00:15:13.065
I'd never say that to you. Mr. Ko.

154
00:15:13.565 --> 00:15:15.526
Don't even say my name. okay?

155
00:15:16.276 --> 00:15:20.406
It's my own damn fault for letting him
into my family in the first place!

156
00:15:20.489 --> 00:15:24.493
How are you so sure
that Taeju really did it?

157
00:15:24.576 --> 00:15:28.455
I saw with my own two eyes in that video.

158
00:15:28.539 --> 00:15:30.833
how he asked the guy
to get rid of my daughter!

159
00:15:30.916 --> 00:15:32.543
There's no way he did that.

160
00:15:32.626 --> 00:15:37.047
What. you think I'm lying to you
when my daughter's life is on the line?

161
00:15:40.259 --> 00:15:42.136
He's telling the truth.

162
00:15:44.304 --> 00:15:46.515
I saw the video with him.

163
00:16:11.290 --> 00:16:12.541
That's pretty.

164
00:17:07.179 --> 00:17:08.263
Did you sleep well?

165
00:17:12.810 --> 00:17:16.188
I came by earlier.
but you were sleeping so soundly.

166
00:17:17.064 --> 00:17:19.566
How's your neck? Let me take a look.

167
00:17:22.611 --> 00:17:25.656
This is going to take a while to heal.

168
00:17:32.287 --> 00:17:33.789
Here. Try putting this on it.

169
00:17:36.458 --> 00:17:37.918
LIQUID PAIN RELIEVER

170
00:17:38.669 --> 00:17:40.129
Come on. take it.

171
00:17:40.212 --> 00:17:41.839
You'll die when the time comes.

172
00:17:41.922 --> 00:17:44.091
so you might as well
spare yourself the pain now.

173
00:17:44.591 --> 00:17:45.801
Oh. well.

174
00:17:54.768 --> 00:17:56.812
This is how much time you have left.

175
00:18:01.775 --> 00:18:05.070
When the sand runs out. you're dead.

176
00:18:08.449 --> 00:18:10.868
You all right?

177
00:18:12.828 --> 00:18:14.413
Geez. okay.

178
00:18:16.748 --> 00:18:19.877
Right. Apparently. the nuns use this
when they pray at the convent.

179
00:18:19.960 --> 00:18:22.921
You should try praying
if you ever get bored.

180
00:18:24.131 --> 00:18:25.466
Who knows?

181
00:18:25.549 --> 00:18:29.094
You might impress God enough
to get you out of here.

182
00:18:29.595 --> 00:18:32.139
Why are you doing this to me?

183
00:18:43.901 --> 00:18:44.902
Use this. okay?

184
00:18:50.741 --> 00:18:53.702
Why are you doing this to me?

185
00:18:53.785 --> 00:18:56.330
What did I do to deserve this?

186
00:18:56.413 --> 00:18:59.124
What the hell do you want from me?

187
00:19:13.096 --> 00:19:17.017
That driver you'd never seen
before has probably gotten away by now.

188
00:19:18.727 --> 00:19:21.104
Until when do you plan on playing dumb?

189
00:19:23.148 --> 00:19:28.278
<i>If you want to find your wife.
come to 543-7. Shinyu-dong by 11 p.m.</i>

190
00:19:33.492 --> 00:19:34.826
Mr. Kang!

191
00:19:35.911 --> 00:19:37.496
We need you to focus here!

192
00:19:43.710 --> 00:19:46.380
We found this in the trunk of your car.

193
00:19:47.214 --> 00:19:49.424
INSIDE THE TRUNK
OF THE SUSPECT'S VEHICLE

194
00:19:50.092 --> 00:19:51.718
Even the blood splatter matches.

195
00:19:52.344 --> 00:19:53.345
Isn't that funny?

196
00:19:54.263 --> 00:19:57.724
I mean. how could this
have made it into your car?

197
00:19:59.268 --> 00:20:01.228
<i>I said. did you bring my billion won?</i>

198
00:20:20.330 --> 00:20:21.373
I have no idea.

199
00:20:21.456 --> 00:20:22.457
"No idea." huh?

200
00:20:22.541 --> 00:20:25.711
You were there
when the photo was taken. weren't you?

201
00:20:27.296 --> 00:20:30.132
Obviously. he left it in my trunk
without me knowing.

202
00:20:30.215 --> 00:20:33.010
It's also obvious
that he sent you that email.

203
00:20:34.720 --> 00:20:35.929
Is that so?

204
00:20:36.013 --> 00:20:39.016
In that case.
where's the memory card for your dashcam?

205
00:20:39.099 --> 00:20:40.517
That'd prove your innocence.

206
00:20:41.643 --> 00:20:43.979
That's… It disappeared.

207
00:20:44.605 --> 00:20:47.482
Yeah. He probably took that too.

208
00:20:47.566 --> 00:20:51.153
Wow. such unfortunate timing. isn't it?

209
00:20:51.903 --> 00:20:55.949
People from the hospital
saw you arguing at the banquet.

210
00:20:57.367 --> 00:21:00.287
Don't tell me this is
a marriage problem gone too far.

211
00:21:01.288 --> 00:21:04.916
SEONGJIN POLICE STATION

212
00:21:37.574 --> 00:21:41.870
The moment we get the lab results back.
you're going to be detained.

213
00:21:43.455 --> 00:21:44.539
So come on.

214
00:21:45.040 --> 00:21:47.084
It's not too late to come clean.

215
00:21:48.126 --> 00:21:51.755
It's in your best interest
to keep Ms. Ko alive.

216
00:21:52.297 --> 00:21:53.382
Isn't that right?

217
00:22:12.150 --> 00:22:13.151
Do it now.

218
00:22:23.453 --> 00:22:25.664
What is going on today?

219
00:22:26.707 --> 00:22:27.916
I'll go check it out.

220
00:22:30.252 --> 00:22:33.088
Geez.

221
00:22:40.178 --> 00:22:41.179
<i>Remember.</i>

222
00:22:41.680 --> 00:22:47.102
<i>If you want to find your wife.
come to 543-7. Shinyu-dong by 11 p.m.</i>

223
00:22:47.185 --> 00:22:48.228
<i>If you don't.</i>

224
00:22:48.311 --> 00:22:50.397
<i>you may never get to see her again.</i>

225
00:22:52.941 --> 00:22:54.609
What the… Kang Taeju.

226
00:22:55.902 --> 00:22:58.447
Hey. answer me! Kang Taeju!

227
00:23:01.825 --> 00:23:03.577
Can't they do anything about this?

228
00:23:11.460 --> 00:23:13.670
Hey. you know
we've got lines to the annex. right?

229
00:23:13.754 --> 00:23:15.255
-Yes. sir.
-Give them a call.

230
00:23:17.340 --> 00:23:18.759
Come on. man.

231
00:23:18.842 --> 00:23:20.469
Hey. go check out the annex building!

232
00:23:21.219 --> 00:23:23.013
I'll go check it out.

233
00:23:25.056 --> 00:23:26.767
Don't bother. I'll just call them.

234
00:23:31.980 --> 00:23:33.565
-Come over here.
-I'll check it out.

235
00:23:33.648 --> 00:23:35.150
-Kang Taeju!
-Hurry up…

236
00:23:35.233 --> 00:23:36.234
Get him!

237
00:23:37.569 --> 00:23:38.820
Hey. get that punk!

238
00:23:39.488 --> 00:23:40.906
He's going up!

239
00:23:42.699 --> 00:23:44.367
Get him now!

240
00:23:44.451 --> 00:23:46.369
Get him! Move it!

241
00:23:46.453 --> 00:23:48.205
Third floor! Get to the third floor!

242
00:23:48.288 --> 00:23:49.498
Kang Taeju!

243
00:24:01.676 --> 00:24:03.428
-You two take the right side.
-Yes. sir.

244
00:24:03.512 --> 00:24:05.722
You guys take the roof.
The rest of you. with me.

245
00:24:16.358 --> 00:24:18.610
Quick! Go up!

246
00:24:33.750 --> 00:24:35.418
- Did you see him?
- Negative.

247
00:24:53.979 --> 00:24:55.146
What about the rooftop?

248
00:24:55.230 --> 00:24:56.982
- Check out the main gate.
- Yes. sir.

249
00:24:57.065 --> 00:24:59.192
- Come on. let's hurry!
- We'll check it out!

250
00:25:48.325 --> 00:25:52.746
So. guys. we've worked with
a lot of different codes so far. right?

251
00:25:52.829 --> 00:25:54.539
Yeah!

252
00:25:54.623 --> 00:25:57.417
But see. you don't have to memorize
what every single code does

253
00:25:57.500 --> 00:25:59.085
or what you can do with it.

254
00:25:59.169 --> 00:26:02.547
The thing is.
even I don't have all of that memorized.

255
00:26:03.298 --> 00:26:04.674
- But Mr. Noh!
- Yes?

256
00:26:04.758 --> 00:26:07.135
How can we use the codes
if we don't memorize them?

257
00:26:07.218 --> 00:26:08.720
Good point.

258
00:26:08.803 --> 00:26:12.265
When there's need. you can
look up the codes online to practice.

259
00:26:12.349 --> 00:26:15.769
or just let me know anytime you want.
You all have my number. right?

260
00:26:15.852 --> 00:26:17.395
Yeah!

261
00:26:17.479 --> 00:26:20.523
All right. shall we check out
what we'll be learning today?

262
00:26:20.607 --> 00:26:22.108
Okay. turn to page 20.

263
00:27:00.063 --> 00:27:01.648
Are you feeling any better?

264
00:27:24.379 --> 00:27:25.672
I don't know.

265
00:27:26.965 --> 00:27:28.216
I'm telling you.

266
00:27:28.299 --> 00:27:30.635
It's going to get a lot worse.

267
00:27:30.719 --> 00:27:35.098
It only gets scarier
and more frightening over time.

268
00:27:35.807 --> 00:27:38.268
No one could ever get used to this.

269
00:27:39.185 --> 00:27:40.687
How did he get you?

270
00:27:41.229 --> 00:27:43.189
I got jumped from behind

271
00:27:43.273 --> 00:27:45.567
while I was leaving
a fortune teller's place.

272
00:27:46.317 --> 00:27:48.611
I was sleeping at home.

273
00:27:49.654 --> 00:27:52.073
and he was standing right there
when I opened my eyes.

274
00:27:53.450 --> 00:27:55.785
But I have no idea
why he's doing this to me.

275
00:27:56.286 --> 00:28:00.582
I think I have an idea
as to why this is happening to me.

276
00:28:01.666 --> 00:28:02.667
Why's that?

277
00:28:03.251 --> 00:28:06.379
See. I did a bad thing.

278
00:28:09.340 --> 00:28:10.759
"A bad thing"?

279
00:28:10.842 --> 00:28:15.889
There's a spirit we serve in our home.
and I turned my back on them.

280
00:28:16.806 --> 00:28:19.684
Things got so rough.
and I couldn't see a way forward.

281
00:28:19.768 --> 00:28:22.604
so I sought out
other shamans out of desperation.

282
00:28:23.855 --> 00:28:26.691
So maybe. do you think

283
00:28:28.234 --> 00:28:30.445
you might have wronged someone?

284
00:28:31.237 --> 00:28:32.906
Maybe you hurt someone.

285
00:28:34.115 --> 00:28:39.454
You know. being here really opened my eyes
to what a horrible thing I'd done.

286
00:28:45.585 --> 00:28:47.003
She's not praying.

287
00:28:52.008 --> 00:28:54.177
All right. guys. Everybody done reading?

288
00:28:54.260 --> 00:28:55.303
MR. NOH'S COMPUTER CLASS

289
00:29:09.484 --> 00:29:11.778
SEONGJIN POLICE STATION

290
00:29:18.618 --> 00:29:19.619
I found him!

291
00:29:23.289 --> 00:29:24.290
Play it back.

292
00:29:30.505 --> 00:29:31.840
He jumped out of that window?

293
00:29:32.465 --> 00:29:34.759
He's lost it. Isn't he a doctor?

294
00:29:35.426 --> 00:29:36.553
Are you admiring the guy?

295
00:29:37.512 --> 00:29:38.680
Get a move on.

296
00:29:38.763 --> 00:29:39.764
Let's roll.

297
00:29:40.348 --> 00:29:41.599
Come on!

298
00:29:46.020 --> 00:29:47.981
Mom. here.

299
00:29:56.823 --> 00:29:57.907
Detective.

300
00:29:57.991 --> 00:30:00.285
What's going on? Where's Taeju?

301
00:30:00.368 --> 00:30:01.536
-He bolted.
-What?

302
00:30:01.619 --> 00:30:03.621
Wait a minute! What are you talking about?

303
00:30:03.705 --> 00:30:05.456
He ran off during the interrogation.

304
00:30:05.540 --> 00:30:06.958
-I…
-What…

305
00:30:08.209 --> 00:30:09.460
-What…
-What is going on?

306
00:30:09.544 --> 00:30:10.920
He ran away?

307
00:30:11.880 --> 00:30:15.967
You said your son is
incapable of doing anything bad.

308
00:30:16.050 --> 00:30:19.679
So why would he run
if he hasn't done anything wrong?

309
00:30:21.347 --> 00:30:23.892
I'm sure he had his reasons.

310
00:30:25.059 --> 00:30:26.686
Just give him some time.

311
00:30:26.769 --> 00:30:28.354
Reasons?

312
00:30:29.355 --> 00:30:31.691
There's no excuse
for running away from the police!

313
00:30:33.067 --> 00:30:34.110
My goodness.

314
00:30:34.819 --> 00:30:36.821
What a mother you are.

315
00:30:37.405 --> 00:30:39.824
What a loving mother!

316
00:30:39.908 --> 00:30:43.661
It's just incredible! Give me a break.

317
00:30:47.540 --> 00:30:50.293
Oh. Mom. Are you okay?

318
00:30:51.210 --> 00:30:53.963
Let's sit you down. There you go.

319
00:30:54.047 --> 00:30:57.175
-Taeyeong.
-Yeah.

320
00:30:57.258 --> 00:31:00.053
-What in the world is happening?
-Exactly.

321
00:31:00.136 --> 00:31:02.138
-Why would he… Why…
-That idiot!

322
00:31:02.221 --> 00:31:05.350
Why did he run away
in a situation like this?

323
00:31:06.601 --> 00:31:07.894
Ugh. geez.

324
00:31:07.977 --> 00:31:09.062
It's okay.

325
00:31:10.313 --> 00:31:12.482
WOORI TOGETHER MEDICAL CENTER

326
00:31:40.635 --> 00:31:41.886
Hey. excuse me.

327
00:31:42.804 --> 00:31:44.347
Oh. hey. It's just me.

328
00:31:44.430 --> 00:31:46.057
Oh. hello. Dr. Kang.

329
00:31:46.891 --> 00:31:48.309
What are you doing here so late?

330
00:31:50.311 --> 00:31:52.105
I forgot something in my office.

331
00:31:53.356 --> 00:31:55.149
-Have a good one.
-You too.

332
00:32:43.448 --> 00:32:45.158
OPERATING ROOM

333
00:32:48.411 --> 00:32:49.704
ACCESS GRANTED

334
00:32:49.787 --> 00:32:55.585
RESTRICTED AREA
AUTHORIZED PERSONNEL ONLY

335
00:34:04.737 --> 00:34:06.155
Geez. you scared me.

336
00:34:06.239 --> 00:34:09.075
-Hey. Chiung.
-What are you doing here so late?

337
00:34:09.158 --> 00:34:11.786
You know.
I just left something in the office.

338
00:34:12.912 --> 00:34:14.914
Must be pretty damn important.

339
00:34:15.581 --> 00:34:17.875
What about you? What are you doing here?

340
00:34:17.959 --> 00:34:19.877
I'm on call tonight.

341
00:34:19.961 --> 00:34:22.421
Pharmacy wanted me
to check the anesthetics inventory.

342
00:34:22.505 --> 00:34:24.215
I see.

343
00:34:25.049 --> 00:34:27.301
-Hang in there. then. See you.
-Okay.

344
00:34:29.679 --> 00:34:30.721
Chiung.

345
00:34:31.722 --> 00:34:32.723
Hmm?

346
00:34:32.807 --> 00:34:34.434
What? You got something to say?

347
00:34:36.102 --> 00:34:37.186
Well. I…

348
00:34:38.229 --> 00:34:40.481
I had a bit of an incident today.

349
00:34:40.565 --> 00:34:41.774
Oh. what happened?

350
00:34:42.400 --> 00:34:44.777
Well. it's kind of serious.

351
00:34:45.820 --> 00:34:46.821
Yeah.

352
00:34:47.780 --> 00:34:50.158
Now that you mention it.
you're a mess. man.

353
00:34:50.241 --> 00:34:51.993
What's going on?

354
00:34:54.454 --> 00:34:55.496
It's nothing.

355
00:34:55.580 --> 00:34:56.831
I'll tell you later.

356
00:34:57.457 --> 00:35:01.169
You know. actually…
Could you lend me your car?

357
00:35:02.170 --> 00:35:04.505
My car? Where's yours?

358
00:35:05.339 --> 00:35:09.010
Mine's… What's with all the questions?
You'll get it back tomorrow.

359
00:35:10.052 --> 00:35:11.387
Yeah. whatever.

360
00:35:11.471 --> 00:35:13.055
It's on level B3.

361
00:35:15.266 --> 00:35:16.934
Is it something to do with your wife?

362
00:35:17.977 --> 00:35:18.978
It is. right?

363
00:35:20.021 --> 00:35:22.565
Something's going on. right? What is it?

364
00:35:27.278 --> 00:35:28.654
It's okay. You can tell me.

365
00:35:29.780 --> 00:35:30.990
The thing is…

366
00:35:32.492 --> 00:35:33.493
Seyun got…

367
00:35:37.205 --> 00:35:38.748
Sorry. let me take this real quick.

368
00:35:41.459 --> 00:35:42.460
This is Choi.

369
00:35:45.087 --> 00:35:46.923
Hey. Dr. Choi. it's me.

370
00:35:47.006 --> 00:35:48.925
I'll cut right to the chase.

371
00:35:49.008 --> 00:35:51.177
Have you heard from Taeju at all?

372
00:35:51.260 --> 00:35:53.679
-Yeah. what a coincidence.
-<i>What?</i>

373
00:35:53.763 --> 00:35:55.431
Are you with him right now?

374
00:35:56.974 --> 00:35:58.476
Answer with "yes" or "no" only.

375
00:36:00.019 --> 00:36:01.103
Yes.

376
00:36:04.482 --> 00:36:07.318
<i>Where are you right now? At the hospital?</i>

377
00:36:07.401 --> 00:36:08.402
Yes.

378
00:36:08.486 --> 00:36:10.321
Okay. he's at the hospital.

379
00:36:10.404 --> 00:36:13.074
I'll make the call to the police then.

380
00:36:13.157 --> 00:36:15.284
Listen to me carefully. Dr. Choi.

381
00:36:16.118 --> 00:36:19.539
That bastard kidnapped my daughter!

382
00:36:29.507 --> 00:36:30.841
What are you talking about?

383
00:36:30.925 --> 00:36:32.635
<i>He’s got her hidden somewhere.</i>

384
00:36:32.718 --> 00:36:35.930
<i>He just bolted from the police station
while they were interrogating him!</i>

385
00:36:37.014 --> 00:36:39.976
<i>To find Seyun.
we have to catch that bastard.</i>

386
00:36:40.893 --> 00:36:43.229
<i>The police are on their way.</i>

387
00:36:43.312 --> 00:36:45.648
<i>so you have to keep him there.
no matter what.</i>

388
00:36:45.731 --> 00:36:46.732
<i>Do you hear me?</i>

389
00:36:48.859 --> 00:36:50.236
Yeah. I got it.

390
00:36:54.865 --> 00:36:58.619
Chiung. I'm so sorry. I'll explain later!

391
00:36:58.703 --> 00:37:00.454
Have you lost your mind?

392
00:37:03.916 --> 00:37:05.543
-Hey. who's there?
-Go. stop him.

393
00:37:05.626 --> 00:37:06.877
Dr. Choi?

394
00:37:07.878 --> 00:37:09.005
Dr. Choi!

395
00:37:09.088 --> 00:37:10.923
I said. go and stop Dr. Kang!

396
00:37:12.049 --> 00:37:13.259
Okay!

397
00:37:43.956 --> 00:37:45.207
-Hello.
-Dr. Kang.

398
00:37:45.291 --> 00:37:46.834
-What are you doing?
-Sorry.

399
00:37:46.917 --> 00:37:48.336
Just get out for a minute.

400
00:37:48.419 --> 00:37:50.463
-Right. yeah.
-We'll talk outside the car.

401
00:37:50.546 --> 00:37:52.965
-This seat belt just won't…
-Yeah. I'll do it for you.

402
00:37:53.049 --> 00:37:54.383
There we go. Come on.

403
00:37:54.467 --> 00:37:56.510
-No. listen. this is…
-It's just for a moment.

404
00:37:56.594 --> 00:37:59.347
- Look. Chief. You got it all wrong.
- I'm sure I do.

405
00:37:59.430 --> 00:38:00.431
I don't think so.

406
00:38:00.514 --> 00:38:02.808
-I understand.
-Could you… I said. you can't go.

407
00:38:02.892 --> 00:38:05.227
-I'll tell you later. I swear.
-Come on.

408
00:38:05.311 --> 00:38:06.312
I got it.

409
00:38:06.395 --> 00:38:09.815
I'll radio upstairs. so you can talk
after I hear from them. Stay right there.

410
00:38:13.069 --> 00:38:14.403
Dr. Kang!

411
00:38:14.487 --> 00:38:16.781
Stay away!

412
00:38:17.698 --> 00:38:18.991
I'm so sorry!

413
00:38:22.703 --> 00:38:24.664
Do your homework. Yuhyeon. Okay?

414
00:38:24.747 --> 00:38:25.831
-Okay. fine!
-Bye.

415
00:38:25.915 --> 00:38:28.292
- Bye.
- See you.

416
00:38:31.545 --> 00:38:32.546
Oh. hey. what's up?

417
00:38:37.051 --> 00:38:41.097
It's been blinking on and off
for the past few days.

418
00:38:41.180 --> 00:38:44.558
and now it's completely stopped working.

419
00:38:45.518 --> 00:38:49.146
I couldn't take any payments.
It's really been a nightmare.

420
00:38:49.855 --> 00:38:51.023
What do you think?

421
00:38:51.107 --> 00:38:52.692
You think you can fix it?

422
00:38:52.775 --> 00:38:55.361
See. It's all the dust
that's built up in here.

423
00:38:55.444 --> 00:38:56.821
That's why it wouldn't read.

424
00:38:56.904 --> 00:38:58.864
-It should work now.
-Ah.

425
00:39:01.951 --> 00:39:02.952
There it is.

426
00:39:04.120 --> 00:39:07.373
My goodness! Now it works. huh?

427
00:39:07.456 --> 00:39:08.666
How much do I owe you?

428
00:39:08.749 --> 00:39:10.376
Oh. don't worry about it.

429
00:39:10.459 --> 00:39:14.130
Oh. come on. I feel bad
you help me out all the time.

430
00:39:14.213 --> 00:39:17.550
What's there to feel bad about?
Plus. who else would you get help from?

431
00:39:18.676 --> 00:39:21.721
Well. thank you.
Why don't you stay for dinner then?

432
00:39:22.304 --> 00:39:24.890
-Have a seat right here. okay?
-No. it's fine.

433
00:39:25.766 --> 00:39:27.852
-Come on. Have a seat. Okay?
-You don't have to.

434
00:39:30.104 --> 00:39:31.313
Thank you so much.

435
00:39:31.397 --> 00:39:34.525
{\an8}JANG SUNDAEGUK

436
00:39:34.608 --> 00:39:37.153
Sweetheart. can you set his table?

437
00:39:37.236 --> 00:39:38.320
Okay. Grandma.

438
00:39:38.404 --> 00:39:40.740
Is that your granddaughter
you always talk about?

439
00:39:40.823 --> 00:39:42.032
Yes. she is.

440
00:39:46.954 --> 00:39:50.124
Your grandmother's told me all about you.

441
00:39:50.791 --> 00:39:52.126
-Nice to meet you.
-Likewise.

442
00:39:52.710 --> 00:39:57.214
You know Woori Together Medical Center?
She works as a nurse there.

443
00:39:57.840 --> 00:39:59.467
Oh.

444
00:39:59.550 --> 00:40:00.968
Yeah. I've been there.

445
00:40:01.051 --> 00:40:05.014
She helps me out
whenever she can. after her shift.

446
00:40:05.097 --> 00:40:08.350
She's not like
the other young people these days.

447
00:40:09.310 --> 00:40:10.770
I've raised a fine girl.

448
00:40:12.772 --> 00:40:15.191
You really have. You must be proud of her.

449
00:40:15.775 --> 00:40:18.527
Just sit tight.
and I'll get your food ready.

450
00:40:18.611 --> 00:40:20.154
Thank you.

451
00:40:20.237 --> 00:40:22.364
That's 22.000 won.
Do you need your receipt?

452
00:40:22.448 --> 00:40:24.617
- It's fine.
- <i>Moving on to our next story…</i>

453
00:40:24.700 --> 00:40:25.701
- Bye.
- Thank you.

454
00:40:25.785 --> 00:40:28.120
<i>An armed robbery occurred
at a convenience store</i>

455
00:40:28.204 --> 00:40:30.790
<i>in Jungang-dong. Seongjin-gu.
around 8:40 tonight.</i>

456
00:40:30.873 --> 00:40:34.293
<i>Police took over 20 minutes to arrive
after receiving the report.</i>

457
00:40:34.376 --> 00:40:36.128
<i>allowing the suspect to escape.</i>

458
00:40:36.212 --> 00:40:39.840
<i>An unexplained power outage
at Seongjin Police Station</i>

459
00:40:39.924 --> 00:40:42.885
<i>disrupted communications.
delaying the initial response.</i>

460
00:40:49.391 --> 00:40:52.353
I mean. he did seem a little off
when he came in.

461
00:40:52.436 --> 00:40:54.188
but I didn't think much of it.

462
00:40:54.772 --> 00:40:58.984
And then Dr. Choi told me
to stop him. so I did.

463
00:40:59.068 --> 00:41:02.696
But then. Dr. Kang took my pepper gun
and sprayed me with it.

464
00:41:03.656 --> 00:41:05.574
My eyes haven't stopped watering since.

465
00:41:06.367 --> 00:41:07.409
You all right?

466
00:41:08.369 --> 00:41:09.870
Yeah. I'm fine.

467
00:41:10.746 --> 00:41:11.831
But…

468
00:41:11.914 --> 00:41:15.918
Listen. They're missing about six vials
of anesthetics in the operating room safe.

469
00:41:16.710 --> 00:41:18.170
They're missing some scalpels

470
00:41:18.254 --> 00:41:20.506
and surgical instruments
for cutting through bones.

471
00:41:21.090 --> 00:41:22.091
Right.

472
00:41:22.967 --> 00:41:25.094
When are you going to catch this bastard?

473
00:41:25.928 --> 00:41:28.639
What if something happens to my daughter?

474
00:41:28.722 --> 00:41:30.599
Just a moment. Excuse me.

475
00:41:32.226 --> 00:41:33.227
Yes. talk.

476
00:41:33.769 --> 00:41:37.022
{\an8}Yeah. Captain. It looks like
after carjacking the vehicle.

477
00:41:37.106 --> 00:41:39.608
Kang drove out of the parking garage
at 9:17 p.m..

478
00:41:39.692 --> 00:41:41.902
{\an8}and took a turn
toward Angok-ro at 9:18 p.m.

479
00:41:41.986 --> 00:41:43.445
He couldn't have gotten far then.

480
00:41:43.529 --> 00:41:46.907
Put out an APB on the vehicle
and have dispatch track him using WASS.

481
00:41:46.991 --> 00:41:49.285
Alert all nearby units for backup.

482
00:41:49.368 --> 00:41:51.537
-I'm moving out now.
-Copy that.

483
00:41:52.496 --> 00:41:54.748
It's go time. Let's roll.

484
00:41:58.669 --> 00:42:02.423
If you can't save my daughter.
I will hold you accountable.

485
00:42:03.173 --> 00:42:04.633
We'll do everything we can.

486
00:42:13.017 --> 00:42:14.184
Move it!

487
00:42:21.066 --> 00:42:23.152
-Head toward Angok-ro.
-Copy that.

488
00:42:39.001 --> 00:42:40.419
You bastard.

489
00:42:41.086 --> 00:42:42.588
You bastard.

490
00:42:43.339 --> 00:42:44.757
You bastard.

491
00:42:45.257 --> 00:42:46.383
You scumbag.

492
00:42:58.938 --> 00:43:00.439
You all right?

493
00:43:02.024 --> 00:43:03.859
He's such a bastard.

494
00:43:08.238 --> 00:43:09.239
Right.

495
00:43:11.700 --> 00:43:13.994
That's why he does these things.

496
00:43:15.371 --> 00:43:16.622
No. not him.

497
00:43:17.122 --> 00:43:18.457
I'm talking about my husband.

498
00:43:21.752 --> 00:43:22.753
What?

499
00:43:24.838 --> 00:43:27.925
The kidnapper called my husband
and told him I was kidnapped.

500
00:43:28.008 --> 00:43:31.512
but he just said. "Do whatever
you want with her" and hung up.

501
00:43:32.346 --> 00:43:34.264
He hasn't even picked up since.

502
00:43:40.479 --> 00:43:43.232
But the kidnapper
may not have been telling the truth.

503
00:43:44.066 --> 00:43:45.567
Maybe he made it all up.

504
00:43:47.319 --> 00:43:50.155
I had a fight
with my husband before I left.

505
00:43:50.864 --> 00:43:52.116
He said it to my face.

506
00:43:52.950 --> 00:43:55.494
That he was glad we didn't have children.

507
00:43:55.577 --> 00:43:58.080
That he wishes I would just die already.

508
00:43:59.790 --> 00:44:03.460
Me dying here is
exactly what he'd wish for.

509
00:44:04.712 --> 00:44:06.547
He'd be happy if I died.

510
00:44:07.715 --> 00:44:11.093
Was that your husband who was crying

511
00:44:11.802 --> 00:44:15.389
on the phone earlier?

512
00:44:24.314 --> 00:44:25.691
Yes. it was.

513
00:44:27.359 --> 00:44:30.529
You guys must have had
a good marriage going.

514
00:44:30.612 --> 00:44:33.240
We're both stuck here.
but I got to say. I'm jealous.

515
00:44:35.617 --> 00:44:36.785
What's your name?

516
00:44:38.078 --> 00:44:39.913
Mine's Lee Seonja.

517
00:44:42.666 --> 00:44:44.084
My name is Ko Seyun.

518
00:44:46.587 --> 00:44:48.213
Hey. Seyun.

519
00:44:48.297 --> 00:44:50.424
Can you do me a favor?

520
00:44:52.051 --> 00:44:53.052
What is it?

521
00:44:54.136 --> 00:44:56.388
When you get out of here.

522
00:44:57.222 --> 00:44:59.933
can you let the police know

523
00:45:00.017 --> 00:45:04.563
that Lee Seonja from Songmu-dong
died in this place?

524
00:45:06.398 --> 00:45:08.567
I don't have much time left.

525
00:45:09.234 --> 00:45:11.945
I'm going to die soon.

526
00:45:22.664 --> 00:45:24.249
PUBLIC SERVICE CENTER

527
00:45:27.252 --> 00:45:28.253
Hello?

528
00:45:28.337 --> 00:45:30.589
Taeyeong. it's me.

529
00:45:40.390 --> 00:45:41.391
You idiot.

530
00:45:42.518 --> 00:45:43.852
Where are you?

531
00:45:43.936 --> 00:45:45.145
What's going on?

532
00:45:45.729 --> 00:45:47.147
<i>Why did you run away?</i>

533
00:45:47.731 --> 00:45:50.484
I'll explain later.
How's Mom? Is she doing okay?

534
00:45:50.567 --> 00:45:52.027
<i>Of course she isn't.</i>

535
00:45:52.111 --> 00:45:53.946
She almost fainted because of you.

536
00:45:54.446 --> 00:45:56.657
Why would you run from the police?

537
00:45:57.366 --> 00:45:58.367
Hold on.

538
00:45:58.909 --> 00:45:59.993
It wasn't you. was it?

539
00:46:01.036 --> 00:46:02.079
Of course not.

540
00:46:03.664 --> 00:46:05.624
It wasn't me. but…

541
00:46:07.417 --> 00:46:09.336
She did get kidnapped because of me.

542
00:46:11.421 --> 00:46:13.298
I have to save Seyun.

543
00:46:13.382 --> 00:46:14.883
<i>What are you talking about?</i>

544
00:46:14.967 --> 00:46:17.094
You should be getting help
from the police.

545
00:46:17.177 --> 00:46:18.637
You can't do this on your own.

546
00:46:18.720 --> 00:46:21.098
<i>You think you're some kind of superhero?</i>

547
00:46:23.142 --> 00:46:24.143
Yeah.

548
00:46:25.477 --> 00:46:27.521
I kind of wish I was.

549
00:46:28.188 --> 00:46:29.231
Hey. listen.

550
00:46:29.898 --> 00:46:31.650
Talk to Mom for me. okay?

551
00:46:32.234 --> 00:46:34.153
<i>Get back here and tell her yourself.</i>

552
00:46:34.236 --> 00:46:37.239
If you didn't do it.
it'll all be revealed in time. right?

553
00:46:38.699 --> 00:46:40.534
Don't go making things worse. man.

554
00:46:40.617 --> 00:46:43.328
Listen to your big brother. Taeju. Okay?

555
00:46:45.747 --> 00:46:46.832
Taeju?

556
00:46:47.416 --> 00:46:48.500
Taeju.

557
00:46:50.836 --> 00:46:53.213
Taeju. where are you now?

558
00:46:53.755 --> 00:46:55.632
You're not hurt. are you?

559
00:46:56.175 --> 00:46:58.135
<i>Hey. Mom. I'm fine.</i>

560
00:47:00.762 --> 00:47:02.347
But I can't go back there right now.

561
00:47:02.431 --> 00:47:05.058
Seyun will be in more danger
if I stay at the station.

562
00:47:05.142 --> 00:47:06.768
<i>What are you talking about?</i>

563
00:47:06.852 --> 00:47:11.064
Why would you being at the station
put Seyun in danger?

564
00:47:11.607 --> 00:47:12.608
Taeju.

565
00:47:13.483 --> 00:47:14.985
Come back. It's not too late.

566
00:47:18.030 --> 00:47:19.031
Mom. just…

567
00:47:20.449 --> 00:47:24.161
Just trust me and give me some time.
I promise I'll bring Seyun home.

568
00:47:24.244 --> 00:47:26.288
<i>Taeju.</i>

569
00:47:30.709 --> 00:47:32.377
-Taeju…
-What is it. Mom?

570
00:47:32.461 --> 00:47:33.754
What did he say?

571
00:47:52.064 --> 00:47:54.066
RED LIGHT AND SPEEDING
SURVEILLANCE CAMERA

572
00:47:57.653 --> 00:48:00.030
Captain. we got an update
on Kang's location.

573
00:48:00.113 --> 00:48:02.074
-Where?
-He was at Deoksam Intersection

574
00:48:02.157 --> 00:48:03.700
at 9:46 p.m.

575
00:48:03.784 --> 00:48:05.118
Heading that way.

576
00:50:31.014 --> 00:50:32.265
It's working.

577
00:51:33.452 --> 00:51:35.912
-Just make it quick.
-Yeah. We'd like to. but…

578
00:51:43.170 --> 00:51:45.922
Yujeong Intersection.
Plate number 682T 1228.

579
00:51:46.006 --> 00:51:47.549
Visual on suspect vehicle.

580
00:51:50.177 --> 00:51:51.178
Hey.

581
00:51:51.845 --> 00:51:53.013
Yujeong Intersection?

582
00:51:53.847 --> 00:51:54.848
Okay. on my way.

583
00:51:55.390 --> 00:51:57.350
Let's take the long way
through Shinyu-dong.

584
00:51:57.434 --> 00:51:58.435
Copy that.

585
00:51:58.518 --> 00:52:00.812
- Send backup to Yujeong Intersection.
- Sir.

586
00:52:01.396 --> 00:52:03.482
<i>Suspect vehicle
is on Yujeong Intersection.</i>

587
00:52:03.565 --> 00:52:05.233
<i>All nearby units. respond for backup.</i>

588
00:52:28.089 --> 00:52:30.717
<i>Plate number 1228. please pull over.</i>

589
00:52:31.218 --> 00:52:32.969
<i>Pull over. 1228.</i>

590
00:52:33.553 --> 00:52:34.679
<i>I repeat. 1228.</i>

591
00:52:43.271 --> 00:52:45.941
<i>I repeat. Pull over. 1228.</i>

592
00:52:46.733 --> 00:52:49.152
<i>I repeat. 1228. Stop the vehicle.</i>

593
00:53:10.924 --> 00:53:13.134
<i>Suspect vehicle is heading
toward Shinyu-dong.</i>

594
00:53:14.970 --> 00:53:16.972
<i>Units two and three. in pursuit.</i>

595
00:53:31.861 --> 00:53:32.988
Kang Taeju!

596
00:53:33.989 --> 00:53:35.323
Pull over right now!

597
00:53:35.407 --> 00:53:37.367
Stop the car. you bastard!
This is dangerous!

598
00:53:38.702 --> 00:53:39.869
Kang Taeju!

599
00:53:40.745 --> 00:53:42.038
Stop being so reckless!

600
00:53:44.791 --> 00:53:46.001
Pull over!

601
00:53:48.420 --> 00:53:49.421
Kang Taeju!

602
00:53:49.504 --> 00:53:51.172
Get in front of him.

603
00:53:51.840 --> 00:53:53.633
Cut him off! Get in front of him!

604
00:54:01.266 --> 00:54:02.892
Darn it.

605
00:54:24.414 --> 00:54:25.707
Turn around! Step on it!

606
00:54:25.790 --> 00:54:28.460
<i>Control. we lost
the suspect vehicle during pursuit.</i>

607
00:54:28.543 --> 00:54:29.961
<i>Plate number 1228.</i>

608
00:55:34.067 --> 00:55:35.318
Kang Taeju!

609
00:55:35.402 --> 00:55:37.904
Stop the car! Stop!

610
00:55:37.987 --> 00:55:39.739
You bastard!

611
00:55:39.823 --> 00:55:42.075
Hey! Kang Taeju!

612
00:58:25.071 --> 00:58:29.909
THE HUSBAND

613
00:59:10.033 --> 00:59:11.326
{\an8}<i>Put out an APB on Kang Taeju.</i>

614
00:59:11.409 --> 00:59:13.870
{\an8}<i>A standoff erupted
between police and a neurosurgeon</i>

615
00:59:13.953 --> 00:59:18.166
{\an8}<i>suspected of orchestrating
his wife's kidnapping and murder.</i>

616
00:59:18.249 --> 00:59:20.668
{\an8}What the hell? Where is my wife?

617
00:59:20.752 --> 00:59:23.296
{\an8}-Answer me!
-It's up to you to figure it out now.

618
00:59:23.379 --> 00:59:24.881
{\an8}<i>Are you working with that bastard?</i>

619
00:59:26.257 --> 00:59:31.638
{\an8}<i>I know exactly what you're
thinking and doing. wherever you are.</i>

620
00:59:31.721 --> 00:59:33.431
{\an8}<i>Have you ever killed a person before?</i>

621
00:59:33.514 --> 00:59:35.933
{\an8}<i>For his wife…</i>

622
00:59:36.017 --> 00:59:37.602
{\an8}<i>Could Kang Taeju kill a person?</i>

623
00:59:37.685 --> 00:59:39.062
{\an8}Are you out of your mind?

624
00:59:39.145 --> 00:59:42.023
{\an8}<i>The three billion you have here.
I need you to hand it over to me.</i>

625
00:59:43.024 --> 00:59:45.026
{\an8}Translated by Hyun Sik Yoon
